  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/2f2c2a68beb21b9d3a34056118f79aca.avif?t=1736516627\" width=477 height=196 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a394fadc450a0ae64714c2a176badc47.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>One day you fell into the virtual world and was asked to train an AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/908c10d002354181a72f794bdbec1655.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>This is a danmaku game, but you will not challenge the bullet-hell by yourself. Raise an AI to deal with all kinds of danmaku.<br>On the one hand, you need to upgrade the AI by beating enemies, adjust the AI parameters, and make the AI become more powerful. <br>On the other hand, there is danmaku that AI can't dodge. It is necessary to be familiar with the characteristics of AI and overcome the difficulties through human-machine collaboration.<br><br>Note: The main stages of this game are basically played with the mouse. There is another challenge mode that can be played with the keyboard or gamepad as traditional shmups, but you can be assisted by AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/59c0244533e09bd788e2722626fe9354.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>Lead the AI with mouse, and AI will dodge by herself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.poster.avif?t=1736516627\" width=332 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.webm?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.mp4?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Live2D portrait<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.poster.avif?t=1736516627\" width=218 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.webm?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.mp4?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/2f2c2a68beb21b9d3a34056118f79aca.avif?t=1736516627\" width=477 height=196 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a394fadc450a0ae64714c2a176badc47.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>One day you fell into the virtual world and was asked to train an AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/908c10d002354181a72f794bdbec1655.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>This is a danmaku game, but you will not challenge the bullet-hell by yourself. Raise an AI to deal with all kinds of danmaku.<br>On the one hand, you need to upgrade the AI by beating enemies, adjust the AI parameters, and make the AI become more powerful. <br>On the other hand, there is danmaku that AI can't dodge. It is necessary to be familiar with the characteristics of AI and overcome the difficulties through human-machine collaboration.<br><br>Note: The main stages of this game are basically played with the mouse. There is another challenge mode that can be played with the keyboard or gamepad as traditional shmups, but you can be assisted by AI.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/59c0244533e09bd788e2722626fe9354.webp?t=1736516627\" width=173 height=45 /></span><br>Lead the AI with mouse, and AI will dodge by herself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.poster.avif?t=1736516627\" width=332 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.webm?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/5b5fa05a646717551363a74ecaab3c6f.mp4?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Live2D portrait<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.poster.avif?t=1736516627\" width=218 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.webm?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1250900/extras/a827bb0724e130b89cd2bedce3858c05.mp4?t=1736516627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
